    <tr><td>**TOTAL**</td><td>RM 3,000-4,700</td><td>RM 4,400-7,300</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<strong>As % of Revenue:</strong> 3-6% of gross rental income
<h3>Factors That Increase Premiums</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Ground-floor unit:</strong> +30% (flood risk)</li>
<li><strong>Older building:</strong> +20% (wear & tear)</li>
<li><strong>History of claims:</strong> +25-50%</li>
<li><strong>No flood barriers:</strong> +15%</li>
<li><strong>Beachfront location:</strong> +20%</li>
</ul>
<h3>Ways to Reduce Premiums</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Higher floor:</strong> -15% (2nd floor+)</li>
<li><strong>Storm shutters:</strong> -10%</li>
<li><strong>Flood barriers:</strong> -10%</li>
<li><strong>No claims bonus:</strong> -20% after 3 years</li>
<li><strong>Security system:</strong> -5%</li>
<li><strong>Bundle policies:</strong> -10% (home + auto)</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-8">
<h2>Short-Term Rental Considerations</h2>
<h3>Commercial Use Endorsement</h3>
<p><strong>Required for:</strong> Airbnb, Booking.com, any paid hosting</p>
<p><strong>What It Adds:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Business liability coverage</li>
<li>Guest injury protection</li>
<li>Commercial property coverage</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Cost Increase:</strong> +20-40% on base premium</p>
<p><strong>Alternatives:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Some insurers offer "home-sharing" endorsements (+15-25%)</li>
<li>Commercial policies designed for STRs</li>
</ul>
<h3>Airbnb's Host Protection Insurance</h3>
<p><strong>What It Covers:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Liability for guest bodily injury</li>
<li>Property damage to host's property</li>
<li><strong>Limit:</strong> Up to USD 1 million per occurrence</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>What It DOESN'T Cover:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Your property damage (host protection only)</li>
<li>Intentional acts</li>
<li>Wear & tear</li>
<li>Business interruption</li>
</ul>
<strong>Important:</strong> Airbnb insurance is <strong>supplementary</strong>, not replacement.
<h3>Additional Coverage Options</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Booking.com Protection:</strong> Similar to Airbnb</li>
<li><strong>Host Guarantee:</strong> Platform-specific coverage</li>
<li><strong>Umbrella Policy:</strong> Extra liability (RM 2-5 million)</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-8">
<h2>Flood-Specific Considerations</h2>
<h3>Melaka Coastal Flood Risk Map</h3>
<table>
