    <tr><td>**Elevated Condos (3rd floor+)**</td><td>Low-Medium</td><td>Lower premiums available</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3>Mitigation Measures That Lower Premiums</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Elevated ground floor:</strong> Flood vents, raised platform</li>
<li><strong>Flood barriers:</strong> Removable barriers for doors</li>
<li><strong>Waterproof flooring:</strong> Tile, not carpet</li>
<li><strong>Elevated electrical:</strong> Outlets, switches above flood line</li>
<li><strong>Backup sump pump:</strong> For ground-floor units</li>
<li><strong>Storm shutters:</strong> Protect windows from wind-driven rain</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Premium Reduction:</strong> Up to 25% for implementing 3+ measures</p>
<hr class="my-8">
<h2>Making a Claim: Process & Tips</h2>
<h3>Immediately After Damage</h3>
<ol>
<li><strong>Document everything:</strong> Photos/videos before cleanup</li>
<li><strong>Prevent further damage:</strong> Cover broken windows, pump water (insurer will reimburse)</li>
<li><strong>Contact insurer within 24-48 hours</strong></li>
<li><strong>Separate damaged items:</strong> Don't throw away until approved</li>
</ol>
<h3>Documentation Checklist</h3>
<ul>
<li>[ ] Photos of damage (wide + close-up)</li>
<li>[ ] Video walkthrough</li>
<li>[ ] List of damaged items (with approximate value/age)</li>
<li>[ ] Repair quotes from 3 contractors</li>
<li>[ ] Police report (if theft/vandalism)</li>
<li>[ ] Guest statements (if applicable)</li>
<li>[ ] Weather report (if storm-related)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Timeline Expectations</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Claim filed:</strong> Day 1-2</li>
<li><strong>Adjuster visit:</strong> Day 3-7</li>
<li><strong>Approval:</strong> Day 7-14</li>
<li><strong>Payout:</strong> Day 14-30 (simple), 30-60+ (complex)</li>
<li><strong>Repairs:</strong> Can start once approved</li>
</ul>
<hr class="my-8">
<h2>Common Exclusions to Watch</h2>
<h3>Typical Policy Exclusions</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Wear and tear:</strong> Gradual deterioration not covered</li>
<li><strong>Mold:</strong> Unless from covered water damage</li>
<li><strong>Pest damage:</strong> Termites, rodents (separate policy)</li>
<li><strong>Act of war/terrorism:</strong> Standard exclusion</li>
<li><strong>Nuclear incidents:</strong> Standard exclusion</li>
</ul>
<h3>Airbnb-Specific Exclusions</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Unauthorized guests:</strong> Extra people not on booking</li>
<li><strong>Illegal activities:</strong> Drug use, parties</li>
<li><strong>Intentional damage:</strong> Guest vandalism (guest's responsibility)</li>
<li><strong>Pets:</strong> Unless pet-friendly approved</li>
</ul>
<strong>Protection:</strong> Clear house rules + security deposit
